{"tid":2097340,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣佈黎明卿(#8307)係動物台之恥","createTime":"2020-07-06T17:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T08:17:41.000Z","uid":105678,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a69fc6e7c0414a01489dad6df562010b1b6a748b","tid":2097340,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T17:27:53.000Z","msg":"呢排博狗推周圍推介人地睇來自深圳，點知Netflix同B站都冇<br />\n<br />\n咁本風紀就走去問佢邊度有得睇啦(我唔睇老翻的)，博狗同我講話卡通瘋有。<br />\n<br />\n於是我就去卡通瘋search，搵能埋分類搵咗半粒鐘都唔見人，之後我再問多次係咪真係有，博狗就send張咁嘅圖畀我：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民國文學家魯迅曾經講過：「時間就是生命。無端的空耗別人的時間，其實無異於謀財害命的。」屌你老母，從今日開始，本風紀同博狗之仇不共戴天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d88bf267b602ed5f0f01c98ae66e3de31e54ef","tid":2097340,"uid":29336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"OK"},{"pid":"ff2e828860bd2f044fae9b3446a55347b50d63d1","tid":2097340,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15d88bf267b602ed5f0f01c98ae66e3de31e54ef","tid":2097340,"uid":29336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"OK"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T17:33:57.000Z","msg":"真係嬲"},{"pid":"38fdbf9e00bf86924ca9b27e9fe7d408eb6522f5","tid":2097340,"uid":8307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T17:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h8NiS19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh8NiS19.jpg&h=b460765a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9322f3efb46aa177ae246f8c73d09ebc133497c7","tid":2097340,"uid":191467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T19:33:02.000Z","msg":"一向都係"},{"pid":"5d470625faa612e0968b411a37460452325798d4","tid":2097340,"uid":175208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"自己返深圳咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />